 domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_Cripple_Creek_Scenic_Overlook_-_NARA_-_7718509.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3d/Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_Dedication_Group_at_El_Pueblo_Museum_-_NARA_-_7718502.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3d/Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_Dedication_Group_at_El_Pueblo_Museum_-_NARA_-_7718502.jpg","cap":"Dedication Group at El Pueblo Museum","desc":"Gathered for the dedication of the El Pueblo Museum, this group includes the state coordinator and representatives from all three byways. Location: Location: Pueblo, Colorado (38.267° N 104.610° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by Sally Pearce","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_Dedication_Group_at_El_Pueblo_Museum_-_NARA_-_7718502.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a6/Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_El_Pueblo_Museum_Mural_-_NARA_-_7718505.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a6/Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_El_Pueblo_Museum_Mural_-_NARA_-_7718505.jpg","cap":"El Pueblo Museum Mural","desc":"Hanging in the El Pueblo Museum, this mural depicts different themes from the three byways in the region (Frontier Pathways, Gold Belt Tour, and Highway of Legends). Location: Location: Pueblo, Colorado (38.267° N 104.610° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by Sally Pearce","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_El_Pueblo_Museum_Mural_-_NARA_-_7718505.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2c/Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_Byway_-_El_Pueblo_Visitor_Center_-_NARA_-_7718506.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2c/Frontier_Pathways_Scenic_and_Historic_